title: 2019 Week 16 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 16 Preview
description:
** Stay tuned for the Miami Super Bowl live show announcement at the end of the episode. ** A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal preview each of the week 16 games including the Saints Titans (5:01) the highly anticipated Cowboys at Eagles (13:37) and the Rams at 49ers (38:41).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
